<template>
    <v-card class="ma-6">
        <v-card-title>
            Example listing
        </v-card-title>
        <v-card-subtitle>
            Description
        </v-card-subtitle>
        <v-card-text>
            This is an example listing.
        </v-card-text>
        <v-card-actions>
            <v-spacer/>
            <template v-if="admin">
                <v-btn
                        color="error">
                    Delcine
                </v-btn>
                <v-btn
                        color="success"
                >
                    Approve
                </v-btn>
            </template>
            <v-btn v-else @click="requestInfoBtnClicked">
                Request Info
            </v-btn>

            <RequestInfo  ref="requestInfo"/>
        </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
</template>

<script>
    import RequestInfo from "./RequestInfo";
    export default {
        name: "JobListing",
        // props: {
        //     admin:{
        //         type: Boolean,
        //         default: true
        //     }
        // },
        data: () => ({
            admin: true
        }),
        components:{
            RequestInfo
        },
        methods: {
            requestInfoBtnClicked: function () {
                this.$refs.requestInfo.toggleShown()
            }
        }
    }
</script>
